WEBVTT

1
01:16:05.410 --> 01:16:10.090 
爱的承诺  失去的痛苦  挽回的快乐
The promise of love, the pain of loss, the joy of redemption.

2
01:16:11.210 --> 01:16:15.550 
然后再给他个谜题  看他尽情发挥
Then give him a puzzle and watch him dance.

3
01:16:15.940 --> 01:16:17.290 
别胡说了
Don't be absurd!

4
01:16:17.290 --> 01:16:18.490 
胡说
Absurd?

5
01:16:19.730 --> 01:16:22.690 
帮她破解那封邮件你用了多久
How quickly did you decipher that email for her?

6
01:16:22.870 --> 01:16:24.600 
一分钟吗
Was it the full minute?

7
01:16:24.610 --> 01:16:26.880 
还是你就这么想表现一下
Or were you really eager to impress?

8
01:16:26.880 --> 01:16:29.280 
我看不到5秒钟
I think it was less than five seconds.

9
01:16:30.670 --> 01:16:33.200 
是我让你着了她的道
I drove you into her path.

